*** Ruby Version 1.9.3 or greater must be installed prior to running script (check Ruby Version using "ruby -v")

ex.

`gem install classy`
`require 'classy'` # Depends on implementation

Example: "./sass2less" -- no file specified (will look for .scss files relative to directory)
Example: "./sass2less ~/some-directory/some-other-directory/somefile.scss" -- file specified (will run the script for specified files only)